Revision history for Perl extension Bundle-Perl6

0.12  Thu Jul 25 15:27:43 CEST 2008 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Changed dist style and Changes back to standard. People didn't like it -
       the nail that sticks out gets hammered down.
     - Added standard test files; this will also help with CPANTS.

0.11  Thu, 29 May 2008 12:00:50 -0000 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - Converted Changes file to YAML style
     - .shipit: added Twitter step
     - Makefile.PL: added auto_install() and process_templates()
     - lib/*: converted to template
     - updated t/perlcriticrc
     - removed Perl6::Bible, superseded by Perl6::Doc
     - .shipit: fixed svk.tagpattern
     - tags: NEWFEATURE

0.10  Fri, 19 Oct 2007 18:44:55 +0200 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - fixed copyright to keep Module::Install happy

0.09  Thu, 18 Oct 2007 10:09:39 +0200 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - fixed version requirement of Test::More
     - keep Perl::Critic happy

0.08  Sun, 09 Sep 2007 10:35:00 +0200 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - brought more or less up-to-date

0.07  Wed, 31 Mar 2004 19:14:33 +0200 (Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>)
     - added Perl6::Say modules

